comment12.text=\n\ Create\ evil\ demon\ circles\ randomly\ somewhere\ from\ 2,2\ to\ 23,23\ in\ the\ maze.\n\ @param\ n\ The\ number\ of\ evil\ circles\ to\ be\ created.\n
