comment14.text=\n\ When\ called,\ breaks\ the\ walls\ around\ the\ player's\ current\ room.\ \n\ Does\ not\ break\ the\ boundary\ walls\ on\ the\ edges\ of\ the\ maze\ though.\n
comment15.params=
